      "text": "And that's the end our ways with [[DM.Factions[faction_AppleComputersInterstellar],Apple Computers]].\n\nBut now with Jinxie's pirated [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTekBattleCom],Tek BattleCom]] now back to us, although I'd still prefer to also have the <i>Wolverine</i> 'Mech where it was installed.",
