        "id": "9cfec302617df92f88e86f8c"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "I asked the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAstech],astech]] who gave it back to us about it and she just shrugged her shoulders and said that Apple had recovered several pirated devices over the centuries.\n\nOnly the [[DM.Factions[faction_JinxieBanshees],Banshees]] know its true origin.",
