      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "And our arrangement is that we can't sell or even attempt to copy or even look at the code, otherwise Duke Roberts was very clear and specific on what will happen to us.\n\nHe specifically mentioned hiring the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreBlueStarIrregulars],Blue Star Irregulars]] since Apple has been employing the mercs since the end of the Star League.",
