    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c84f792ad3204041300fe85"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Sumire, he mentioned hiring all three of the Irregulars' regiments, if necessary.\n\nApple is still immensively rich... during the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStarLeague],Star League]] they bought an entire world and renamed it [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMacintosh],Macintosh]] in honor to their first commercial brand.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "They bought a whole planet? You can do that?",
          "conditions": null,
