      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c94128823d3ac2896e9dd44"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Commander, if you are a hunting friend of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreDavionFirstPrince],First Prince]] or a drinking pal with the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreStarLeagueFirstLord],First Lord]] of the Star League, you can pretty much do everything.\n\nEntitled nobles will always act the same way, regardless of their origin.",
      "branches": [
