      "text": "Some of the chips have markings that identify them as being manufactured at [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHachiman],Hachiman]] in the [[DM.Factions[faction_Kurita],Draconis Combine]].\n\nHouse Kurita is making unauthorized copies of Apple's products.",
